<h2>manx.social</h2>
<p><h3>A social platform for the Isle of Man</h3>
<p>Ever find that local discussion is lost in the vastness of Twitter? Or your voice is only reaching those that follow you on Facebook? That is where manx.social comes in - a truly public platform for the Isle of Man.</p>

<p>manx.social lets you get your message across to the island or just tune-in to what's currently happening island-wide.</p>
<p>
Alternatively, connect with others around the world through the federated network and <a href="https://instances.mastodon.xyz/">other instances</a> of Mastodon.</p></p>
