<h2>Mobile Apps</h2>
<p>Apps are available for both Android & iOS. We recommend <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.keylesspalace.tusky">Tusky</a> for Android & <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/amarok-for-mastodon/id1214116200">Amaroq</a> for iOS. More apps are available <a href="https://github.com/tootsuite/documentation/blob/master/Using-Mastodon/Apps.md">here</a>.</p>
